HEADWORD: Conchoidal
<hw>Con*choid"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>concho⟦ium⟧dal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Having
